This directory is intentionally near-empty in the shipped source package.

The application no longer uses local file storage for its database (see
POSTGRESQL_CUTOVER_REPORT.md) — all data lives in PostgreSQL via DATABASE_URL.
The PostgreSQL schema itself lives at server/db/postgres/schema.sql, and the
one-time SQLite-to-PostgreSQL migration utility (for legacy installations
only) lives at scripts/migrate-sqlite-to-postgres.ts.

Historical debug artifacts that previously lived in this folder (a stale
SQLite database file, and two Meta OAuth debug/audit JSON files from earlier
manual testing) have been removed before packaging, since they were runtime
artifacts specific to a prior developer's testing session, not required
migration or sample files for this codebase.
